        <abstract> 
<p>Sends his paper [on glacial lakes, see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">3450</hi>]. Falconer attacked it. Falconer thinks Himalayas confound the theory, but Hooker writes that it explains the absence of lakes there.</p> 
